  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Explain the origin of the shift in frequency and wavelength of the observed wavelength when observer and source moved toward or away from each other</item>
<item>Derive an expression for the relativistic Doppler shift</item>
<item>Apply the Doppler shift equations to real-world examples</item>
</list></md:abstract>
